DNA
File Format Version 1.0

 1 = 500 (1:2.1)                   502 10    // Sensor:      Get Steering Wheel Position
 2 =  14 (1:3.1)                   2         // Offset:      Add offset to achieve 1..3 range (this allows to detect and ignore 0 output as invalid)
 3 = 600                           511       // Actor:       Set Steering Actor
